<ITEM>35 Why is Wales like a neck of mutton?</ITEM>
<ITEM>Becau&s;e 'tis craggy.</ITEM>
<ITEM>36 Why are weather-cocks like the &s;ea?</ITEM>
<ITEM>Becau&s;e they wave.</ITEM>
<ITEM>37 Why are je&s;t-books like being tickled?</ITEM>
